The book is part biography from 10 years living on the road and over 20 years bringing an environmental focus to business. Lose yourself in Dale’s manifesto for saving the planet by looking at energy, transport and food and how he invented a process that pulls carbon from the atmosphere to create Skydiamonds - certified diamonds! So don’t miss out, pick up your Daily Express from Monday March 6, 2023 until Friday March 10, 2023 for your chance to win a stunning full-carat diamond.